modules.description: Handles email composition with subject, body, and recipient fields. Accepts strings for text content and lists for multiple email addresses. Enables direct email launching from an application with predefined message parameters.

Adds and manages email aliases, checks app availability, and constructs email objects with specified headers, body, and attachments. Operates on strings, arrays of strings, and a private email type representing an email composition interface. Used to dynamically build and send emails within a Cordova-based application.
